  const clientIP = req.headers['x-forwarded-for']?.split(',')[0] || req.ip;
  if (!ipRangeCheck(clientIP, ALLOWED_IP_RANGES)) {
    auditLogger.warn('Blocked IP access attempt', { ip: clientIP });
    return res.status(403).end();
  }
  next();
};
```

2. **Application Layer - MFA Enforcement**:
```javascript
// Time-based OTP with strict window
const verified = speakeasy.totp.verify({
  secret: user.mfaSecret,
  encoding: 'base32',
  token: token,
  window: 1 // Only current and adjacent codes
});
```

3. **Session Layer - Secure Configuration**:
```javascript
// __Host- prefix enforces secure cookie requirements
name: '__Host-admin-session',
cookie: {
  secure: true,      // HTTPS only
  httpOnly: true,    // No JavaScript access
  sameSite: 'strict' // No cross-site requests
}
